\n淨係得，「咁政府唔理你點算」<br />\n「人地衝好過你匿係屋企」<br />\n「各有各做」<br />\n根本就冇人答得出為咩要衝同下一步係點<br />\n咁樣係我地想要既行動？"},{"pid":"781799ced7da3610aa44624108d05134d69f6f5a","tid":1271544,"uid":244332,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"cdbb2c8b64f8730ab8d66d2cc8048b5e35d04ec9","tid":1271544,"uid":229289,"like":13,"dislike":12,"score":1,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T06:45:20.000Z","msg":"你答我衝完下下步係咩就得"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T06:50:24.000Z","msg":"我都明衝完係冇用，但唔衝都衝左，敵人就係想我地分化"},{"pid":"e5bca75107f194623e8f6b7cce091aa83e99ead3","tid":1271544,"uid":262322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T06:50:29.000Z","msg":"你講得我錯"},{"pid":"af48d1de30459bc91a3a1120857f4859414ea870","tid":1271544,"uid":31099,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6ee67c0d47fb938292022c851b6b9fe3bcd3d01d","tid":1271544,"uid":265386,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"quote":{"pid":"cdbb2c8b64f8730ab8d66d2cc8048b5e35d04ec9","tid":1271544,"uid":229289,"like":13,"dislike":12,"score":1,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T06:45:20.000Z","msg":"你答我衝完下下步係咩就得"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T06:48:55.000Z","msg":"你答返我你遊行左幾日既下一步係咩先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T06:51:52.000Z","msg":"遊行keep住個人數可以比個世界知道我地香港人仲係不滿 一路令個政府冇籍口話我地對暫緩收貨 仲要冇位比人入<br />\n<br />\n你而家衝對件事咩幫助都冇 仲要比人話你暴力衝擊 你叫我地點信呢班唔係鬼"},{"pid":"03f6fd1e604efdaf4baca618d6abe028deb82afa","tid":1271544,"uid":196329,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6ee67c0d47fb938292022c851b6b9fe3bcd3d01d","tid":1271544,"uid":265386,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"quote":{"pid":"cdbb2c8b64f8730ab8d66d2cc8048b5e35d04ec9","tid":1271544,"uid":229289,"like":13,"dislike":12,"score":1,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T06:45:20.000Z","msg":"你答我衝完下下步係咩就得"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T06:48:55.000Z","msg":"你答返我你遊行左幾日既下一步係咩先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T06:51:57.000Z","msg":"遊